He was removed as a director during a temporary shareholder meeting on November 1, 2024 [cna](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-1) [yahoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-0). 家寧 and her mother responded, stating that all director changes were conducted according to regulations, based on the company's shareholding比例 and operational status, and that Andy remains a registered shareholder [cna](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-1) [udn](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-2).
